				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1eef0aff3a46d1cca51f3da77ccc1479?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">Surya</cite>
